content: Hello! How can I assist you today?

I can help in various tasks such as generating text using AI, searching on Google, searching for images, converting webpages to PDF, taking screenshots of webpages, saving Instagram photos or videos, downloading files, generating PDFs from text, converting text to speech, searching for videos on YouTube, clearing chat history, looking up WHOIS information, providing free internet data for Ufone, extracting text from an image using OCR, and viewing previous chats. Let me know what specific task you need assistance with or if you have any questions!
Koi baat nahi! Agar apko kisi bhi madad ki zaroorat ho toh mujhe bataiye. Main yahan apki khidmat mein hazir hoon!
Kuch aur madad chahiye ya koi sawaal ho toh bataiye, main apki poori koshish karunga aapki madad karne ki.
